results.title: Dogged
results.description: Punisher rescues his dog from the pit fighters who have made off with him.

results.title: Suicide Run Part 1: Terminal Objectives
results.description: Punisher takes on the top leaders of the mob at a super secret meeting and threatens to bring the house down around the lot of them.

results.title: Clock's Ticking
results.description: Punisher takes on a child abductor.

results.title: Suicide Run Part 4: Standing in the Shadows
results.description: With Punisher believed dead under a collapsed building, Lynn and Payback begin trying to fill his shoes.

results.title: Suicide Run Part 10
results.description: With the help of the local sheriff, Punisher kills almost everyone who has chased him to the town of Lastekist; Lynn and Payback recover from injuries and decide to quit the Punisher game; Micro hooks up with Mickey and decides to try and rebuild his Punisher program with someone new.

results.title: Tunnelvision
results.description: Punisher takes down some punks rousting homeless folks.

results.title: Final Entry Part Three: A Journal of the Plague Years
results.description: With the world believing the Punisher dead, Lynn steps into his shoes and takes on VIGIL.

results.title: Final Entry Part 4: Deadstop!
results.description: The Punisher returns to New York; Lynn takes on the mantle of the new Punisher and tangles with Rosalie Carbone's henchmen.

results.title: ["Because you demanded it! Lynn Michaels is The Punisher"]
Stone Dead
results.description: Stone Cold helps put the final nail in VIGIL's coffin; Lynn's father shows up wondering what has happened to his wayward daughter.

results.title: Lynn's Worst Nightmare Comes to Life!
Bound By Blood
results.description: Lynn takes on Heathen, but the job of being the Punisher gets to be too much and she decides to head back to the farm with her father, that is until she and her companions are ambushed by guys in Punisher outfits.

results.title: One Wicked Day
results.description: Lynn wraps up her Punisher business and heads off to a more peaceful life on her father's farm; Castle returns as the true Punisher.
